posts.body:
>>7ba929ca-2ff8-4775-b5be-f289d5a76e92
The first standards were rushed out too quickly, and they didn't scale well.

We need some breakthroughs like they had with video. Everything was a mess - then it collapsed into a few widely used standards. Like certain common codecs used with mkv containers - and finally Google's donation of webm for web use. I'm not a Google fan, but that donation really helped. Too bad we don't have the same common building blocks for secure communications.

Webrtc might be coming close...but there still are problems. Maybe if Loki ever takes off things will turn around.

posts.subject: Civilization has a desperate need to silence know nothing cunts
posts.body:
Like this one.

Melinda Gates thinks she knows better than you, and she's prepared to perform the classic Karen by running to the manager.

While I'll concede that taking the vaccine is likely the best course for old witches such as herself (little to lose and much to gain), attempts to FORCE others to accept vaccinations should be met with deadly response. That's the only means to explain things to busybody people. "Yes you were right - now you're dead." You're so smart.

The correct path is MUCH less clear for those of childbearing age, and it's tragic that noisy bullies like the Gates can inject themselves into these difficult decisions.

The fact that the Gates are still alive and haven't perished in some aircraft disaster would be proof enough for many as to the implausibility of a god. Too many evil people just live so long.....
